Nephritis:

• Nephritis is severe or chronic inflammation of the kidneys
• It can prove fatal if not treated properly

Symptoms to look for:

• Fever
• Dull back pain
• Pain in the urinary tract
• Scanty flow of urine
• Blood in urine

Causes:

• Incorrect eating habits
• Unhealthy lifestyle
• Alcohol
• Smoking
• Weak immune system

